➜河南诗人王琦伟：《吻荷》
http://www.sohu.com/a/420071664_100115135	25249
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/1fbcc54422124d618ff1aed057781eac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《吻荷》（中华新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娇蕊弥香锦鲤惊，跃出碧水赏芳容。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圣腮一吻惜三夏，入腑温情暖九冬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020·9·21</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/c04bf6441597464093d99b12862bf17a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▲【作者简介】：</strong>王琦伟，曾用名王万晗；笔名：梦回桃花源。现任南阳市第三小学教导主任，南阳市优秀教师、南阳市骨干教师，南阳市课改先进个人。喜爱诗歌，兴趣广泛，结识朋友，诚信友善。所写诗歌、散文、游记多在《华夏王氏家园网》和360个人图书馆《高山流水之thy》中发表。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/49a6de58df0644239cdc46b3571efb63.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
