➜张立标（广东）：秋分有寄
http://www.sohu.com/a/420078126_100115135	27015
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f8644f2a8c5e4855aae3a6a361ee9669.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋分有寄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/张立标</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一叶别枝头，迷离已半秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花残风遇冷，夜寂雨添愁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邪疫须留际，营生苦乏筹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜉蝣扛巨浪，无力主沉浮。</p>
